<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA24">
<l>ituvaṉṟē yīcaṉ ṟiruvuruva māmā</l>
<l>ṟituvaṉṟē yeṉṟaṉakkōr cēma - mituvaṉṟē</l>
<l>miṉṉuñ cuṭaruruvāy mīṇṭāyeṉ cintaṉaikkē</l>
<l>yiṉṉuñ cuḻalkiṉṟa tiṅku</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>This, isn’t it, the way the sacred form of the lord is?</l>
<l>This, isn’t it, the one refuge for me? And this, isn’t it,</l>
<l>what still spins here towards my thoughts, being recurrent</l>
<l>as flashing fire form?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
